org.opendaylight.controller.config.manager.impl

Class ConfigRegistryImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.config.manager.impl.ConfigRegistryImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, ConfigRegistry, LookupRegistry, ServiceReferenceReadableRegistry, ConfigRegistryImplMXBean

    @ThreadSafe
public class ConfigRegistryImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable, ConfigRegistryImplMXBean
    Singleton that is responsible for creating and committing Config Transactions. It is registered in Platform MBean Server.
